title: Justin Bieber - All That Matters [ Pre-Release]
description:
Justin Bieber - All That Matters [ Pre-Release]


Over ten weeks, Justin Bieber is releasing a single every Monday. Last week, he released Heart Breaker. Tomorrow, All That Matters will be released. This is what to expect. The quality isn't the best but if you can't wait until tomorrow, this should cover it.


Please remember to support the artist and seed
